== 目的 ==
This template adds an external link to an article in [http://eom.springer.de/default.htm SpringerLink], an online encyclopedia based on the [[数学百科全书]].

==参数==
所有参数都是可选的。
{|  border="1"
|-
|<pre>
{{springer
 | title=
 | id= 
 | last=
 | first=
 | author-link=
 | last2=
 | first2=
 | author2-link=
}}
</pre>
|
* '''title''' (or '''article'''): Title of the article
* '''id''': Springer's id number for the article, which is part of the url. For example the article [http://eom.springer.de/f/f041470.htm http://eom.springer.de/f/f041470.htm] would have id=f/f041470
* '''last''' (or '''last1'''): The first author's surname or last name.
* '''first''' (or '''first1'''): The first author's first or given name(s).
* '''author-link''' (or '''author1-link'''): Title of an existing Wikipedia article about the first author.
* '''last2''',  The second  author's surname or last name, if applicable.
* '''first2''',  The second authors' first or given name(s), if applicable.
* '''author2-link''': Title of an existing Wikipedia article about the second author, if applicable.
|}

== 例子和用法 ==
Suppose you want to add an external link to Springer's [http://www.encyclopediaofmath.org/index.php/Fredholm_theorems article on Fredholm theorems]. The title of this article is "Fredholm theorems" so following the mediawiki page article naming convention the id of the article page would be "Fredholm_theorems". However, because the article is a dynamic document, the version number must be included in the id to complete the citation. The full template id for the current version of this article would be "Fredholm_theorems&oldid=12814".

The code

<nowiki>
* {{SpringerEOM|id=Fredholm_theorems&oldid=12814|title=Fredholm theorems|first=B.V.|last= Khvedelidze}}
</nowiki>

will produce the link
* {{SpringerEOM|id=Fredholm_theorems&oldid=12814|title=Fredholm theorems|first=B.V.|last= Khvedelidze}}

The code

<nowiki>
* {{SpringerEOM|id=Virasoro_algebra&oldid=15975|title=Virasoro algebra|first=V.|last=Kac|authorlink=Victor Kac}}
</nowiki>

will produce

* {{SpringerEOM|id=Virasoro_algebra&oldid=15975|title=Virasoro algebra|first=V.|last=Kac|author-link=Victor Kac}}

The code

<nowiki>
*{{SpringerEOM|id=Index_formulas&oldid=18079|title=Index formulas|first=M.I. |last=Voitsekhovskii|first2=M.A.|last2=Shubin}}
</nowiki>

will produce

*{{SpringerEOM|id=Index_formulas&oldid=18079|title=Index formulas|first=M.I. |last=Voitsekhovskii|first2=M.A.|last2=Shubin}}

The [[Template:Harvard citation|Harvard citation template]]s (with year 2001) will produce internal links; for example
<nowiki>{{harv|Kac|2001}}</nowiki> produces the link {{harv|Kac|2001}}, and <nowiki>{{harv|Voitsekhovskii|Shubin|2001}}</nowiki> produces {{harv|Voitsekhovskii|Shubin|2001}}.

